Install And Run Venkman JavaScript Debugger for Zimbra Desktop
==============================================================

1) Start Zimbra Desktop

2) Shift-F6 to bring out status bar

3) Click on "gear" icon -> Tools -> Add On -> Install...

4) Select javascript_debugger-0.9.87.4.xpi to install 

5) Quit Zimbra Desktop

6) Run Zimbra Desktop from command line, with -venkman argument:

  (assuming default installation paths)

  Mac: 
    /Users/<user>/Library/Zimbra Desktop/Zimbra Desktop.app/Contents/MacOS/prism -venkman

  Windows:
   C:\Program Files\Zimbra\Zimbra Desktop\win32\prism\zdclient.exe -venkman -override <data root>\zdesktop.webapp\override.ini

